{"tid":2217940,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"2隻貓反左面 有冇辦法做和事佬？","createTime":"2020-09-25T23:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T11:43:35.000Z","uid":102949,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0fd241dbdf3f02fc661ab0074e416856c67f97","tid":2217940,"uid":102949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:32:38.000Z","msg":"養緊3隻貓 但3隻都唔fd<br />\n其實有2隻貓仲反左面<br />\n貓A一見到貓B就會 hur佢 <br />\n之後怪叫 如果格硬將佢地放埋一齊 貓A仲會出手打貓B<br />\n貓B善良啲唔會出手 但叫到貓A會西面<br />\n感覺有時佢想和解 但貓A好憎佢<br />\n琴日貓B俾貓A打左幾拳（冇傷既）成個頹左 好唔開心咁<br />\n明明佢地2個幾個月黎個陣都好fd<br />\n成日一齊訓一齊玩<br />\n依家變左咁樣 唔知有冇方法呢<br />\n見人地啲貓好好朋友咁 會一齊玩又痴住"},{"pid":"bf52ab00f319cc96da7dfe9f89bffe757496faa4","tid":2217940,"uid":68478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:41:12.000Z","msg":"再養多隻"},{"pid":"ea5fbbe30e1b2018c3fe9567f8963abbaeef0db8","tid":2217940,"uid":312363,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"放隻狗落去"},{"pid":"1a7b99ba33c7d5bd40e58e9bcc67a744ddde0d31","tid":2217940,"uid":365437,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:48:50.000Z","msg":"喵喵喵喵喵 讀俾佢哋聽"},{"pid":"8a78e172bf32fda754e42ae5ffd0f243d528b3a0","tid":2217940,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:49:27.000Z","msg":"我之前都有兩隻<br />\n幾日之後一齊玩<br />\n一齊奶毛<br />\n大貓仲養埋比細貓食"},{"pid":"deabcf2c9dfbefe71cb33fe7ebb9772781fedb7e","tid":2217940,"uid":3028,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:52:40.000Z","msg":"整個共同敵人俾佢地"},{"pid":"4ab8741d283a3fd4a86fbc9cb7d81ee8965488f9","tid":2217940,"uid":130044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5fbbe30e1b2018c3fe9567f8963abbaeef0db8","tid":2217940,"uid":312363,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T23:46:24.000Z","msg":"放隻狗落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T00:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah